<style>
  html, body {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  h1, h4, p {
    color: #AAAAAA;
  }

  a, a:visited{
    color: white;
  }

  a:hover{
    color:gray;
  }

  .header {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: url(poolside.jpg) no-repeat center center scroll;
    -webkit-background-size: cover;
    -moz-background-size: cover;
    background-size: cover;
    -o-background-size: cover;
  }

  .container {
    margin-top: 50px;
  }

  .title {
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 8em;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align:center;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    transform: translateY(150px);
    opacity: 1;
    animation: move-up 400ms ease-in-out forwards 1;
  }


  .text-vertical-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .margin-bottom {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .album-photo {
    border: 1px solid black;
    border-radius: 2%;
  }

    .page-header {
      text-align:center;
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, Sans-Serif;
      color:rgb(60,60,60);
    }

    .p-content {
      margin-left: 150px;
      margin-right: 150px;
    }

    .p-content p {
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, Sans-Serif;
      color:rgb(60,60,60) !important;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      line-height: 28px;

    }

    .footer h1 {
      color:black !important;
    }

    button {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      height: 50px;
      width: 250px;
      font-size: 11px;
      border-radius: .1em;
      margin-top: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: #4c7d15;
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue",sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.26);
      transition: all 400ms ease-in-out;
      margin: 0 auto;
      margin-left: 44%;
    }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    .title {
      font-size: 50px !important;
    }

    .p-content {
      margin-left: 20px !important;
      margin-right: 20px !important;
    }
  }
</style>


<%= render 'partials/nav' %>
<%= render 'partials/show_logo' %>

<header class="header" style="height:50%">
  <div class="text-vertical-center">
    <h1 class="title">About Us</h1>
    <a href="#about">
      <span class="fa-stack fa-2x">
        <i class="fa fa-square-o fa-stack-2x"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down fa-stack-1x"></i>
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</header>

<div id="about" class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <h1 class="page-header">About</h1>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="p-content">
        <p>Founded in 2012 by Carlos Martinez and Kristen (Vance) Martinez and named by blending their last names together, Vance and Martinez, became the family-owned business, VanMar Lending. Vanmar Lending is a full-service Mortgage Lending Team offering FHA, VA, USDA, Conventional and Jumbo Loan mortgage programs.</p> 

        <p>The Team’s mission and commitment to you is dedicated to facilitating the dream of homeownership by providing you with Five-Star Service. More importantly, our passion and drive is built around winning. Team Vanmar wins at communication, wins at problem solving, wins at getting the job done and getting it done on time. We are confident that you will quickly see how this “winning” attitude separates us from the rest. Please give us a call.we will make it happen for you!</p>
      </div>
      <button>Get Started</button>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<%= render 'partials/footer' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag 'nav' %>